channel.title: 6 Zombie Minigame Errors
channel.description:
I just downloaded Darkclawz v2 and I wanted to compile my source when i got this error.
[code=java] location: class Server src\server\model\players\Client.java:2002: error: cannot find symbol public void execute(CycleEventContainer c) { ^ symbol: class CycleEventContainer src\server\model\npcs\NPCHandler.java:2282: error: cannot find symbol final Client c2 = (Client) PlayerHandler.players[npcs[i].spawned By]; ^ symbol: variable PlayerHandler location: class NPCHandler src\server\model\npcs\NPCHandler.java:2309: error: cannot find symbol Client c = (Client) PlayerHandler.players[npcs[i].spawnedBy]; ^ symbol: variable PlayerHandler location: class NPCHandler src\server\Server.java:78: error: cannot find symbol public static ZombieCaves zombieCaves = new ZombieCaves(); ^ symbol: class ZombieCaves location: class Server Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 6 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Can someone please edit these and send them back thank you. Just ask if you need any more files. Thank You
This is my client.java - http://pastebin.com/gfdBQAd7 This is my npchandler.java - http://pastebin.com/Xu7q0xfns This is my server.java - http://pastebin.com/JyNuKWPY
